{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, streaming platforms such as Netflix and Spotify utilize artificial intelligence (AI) to create playlists and provide recommendations for movies, episodes, or music, augmenting user engagement and overall pleasure (Chen & Chen, 2023).",
    "The implementation of personalized recommendations enhances client retention and contributes to the augmentation of conversion rates and revenue generation for B2C enterprises.",
    "Predictive Analytics for Customer Insights AI-driven predictive analytics is a noteworthy application within business-to-consumer (B2C) digital marketing (Bogers & van den Poel, 2017).",
    "These algorithms predict forthcoming customer behaviors and preferences, empowering marketers to make judgments based on data analysis.",
    "Provost & Fawcett (2013) underscored the significance of predictive analytics in deriving actionable insights from data."
  ]
}